@startuml
!include ../style.puml

participant "Client" as Client
participant "KV Store" as Store

note over Store
  **Physical Keys (Option 2: Wide-Column)**
  [User1_name @ 100]   -> "Alice"
  [User1_status @ 100] -> "Active"
end note

Client -> Store: Update status to "Inactive" (t=200)

note over Store
  **Efficient Partial Update**
  Only the specific column gets a new version!
  
  [User1_name @ 100]   -> "Alice"
  [User1_status @ 200] -> "Inactive"
  [User1_status @ 100] -> "Active"
end note

note right of Store
  **Row Reconstruction (getRow)**
  Prefix Scan: "User1_*" @ AsOf(200)
  => Returns (name="Alice", status="Inactive")
end note
@enduml
